%%{init: {'theme': 'default', 'sequence': {'showSequenceNumbers': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant AuthManager
    participant TokenStore
    participant Browser
    participant GoogleOAuth as Google OAuth Server
    participant ServiceAccount

    User->>CLI: gforms auth login

    CLI->>AuthManager: initiateOAuth()

    AuthManager->>AuthManager: generateCodeVerifier()
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: generateAuthUrl(scopes)

    AuthManager->>Browser: Open auth URL
    Browser->>GoogleOAuth: GET /authorize?scope=...&redirect_uri=localhost
    GoogleOAuth->>User: Show consent screen

    User->>GoogleOAuth: Grant permissions
    GoogleOAuth->>Browser: Redirect to localhost:PORT?code=AUTH_CODE
    Browser->>AuthManager: Receive auth code

    AuthManager->>GoogleOAuth: POST /token (code, code_verifier)
    GoogleOAuth-->>AuthManager: { access_token, refresh_token, expires_in }

    AuthManager->>TokenStore: saveTokens(tokens)
    TokenStore->>TokenStore: write ~/.gforms/credentials.json

    AuthManager-->>CLI: Success
    CLI->>User: "Authenticated successfully"

    Note over User,ServiceAccount: Alternative: Service Account

    User->>CLI: GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=key.json gforms deploy

    CLI->>AuthManager: getAuthClient()
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: checkEnvVar()

    alt Service Account env var set
        AuthManager->>ServiceAccount: loadKeyFile()
        ServiceAccount-->>AuthManager: KeyData
        AuthManager->>ServiceAccount: createJWT(scopes)
        ServiceAccount->>GoogleOAuth: Exchange JWT for access token
        GoogleOAuth-->>ServiceAccount: { access_token }
        ServiceAccount-->>AuthManager: AuthClient
    else No env var, check token store
        AuthManager->>TokenStore: loadTokens()
        alt Token exists and valid
            TokenStore-->>AuthManager: Tokens
        else Token expired
            AuthManager->>GoogleOAuth: POST /token (refresh_token)
            GoogleOAuth-->>AuthManager: New tokens
            AuthManager->>TokenStore: saveTokens()
        else No token
            AuthManager-->>CLI: Error: Run 'gforms auth login'
        end
    end

    AuthManager-->>CLI: AuthClient
